  vibe_description = 'Walking Street is where Pai concentrates its energy. During the day it''s quiet cafes and smoothie shops. At night the road fills with food stalls, buskers, and craft vendors. Everything is cheap and the mood is relaxed. You can walk end to end in ten minutes.',
