  vibe_description = 'West Lake is a big loop of water north of the Old Quarter. The Tran Quoc Pagoda on the southern edge is one of Hanoi''s oldest temples. The surrounding streets have international restaurants and quieter cafes. Cycling around the lake takes about an hour.',
  crowd_vibe = 'Expats, wealthier Hanoians, and joggers circling the lake in the early morning',
